    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Yrsa Frostbane is the Pale Maw Strike Leader who steps into command if Þráinn Ashward falls — an accomplished military commander who is more direct and less ideological than the Inquisitor. She wears battle-worn armor and wields a well-maintained greatsword. Her Command Presence grants passive bonuses to all nearby Pale Maw units, and Rally the Faithful surges them to devastating effectiveness. Relentless, when bloodied, she becomes more dangerous rather than less.</p>",
